      <ui:InvokeCode ContinueOnError="{x:Null}" Code="' ============================================================&#xD;&#xA;' Paso 1: Generar lista de COD con SALDO BANCO no vacío&#xD;&#xA;' ============================================================&#xD;&#xA;Dim lstCodConSaldoBanco As New System.Collections.Generic.List(Of String)()&#xD;&#xA;For Each row As System.Data.DataRow In dtBoletinTemp.Rows&#xD;&#xA;    Dim saldoBanco As String = row(&quot;SALDO BANCO&quot;).ToString().Trim()&#xD;&#xA;    Dim cod As String = row(&quot;COD&quot;).ToString().Trim()&#xD;&#xA;    If Not String.IsNullOrEmpty(saldoBanco) AndAlso Not String.IsNullOrEmpty(cod) Then&#xD;&#xA;        If Not lstCodConSaldoBanco.Contains(cod) Then&#xD;&#xA;            lstCodConSaldoBanco.Add(cod)&#xD;&#xA;        End If&#xD;&#xA;    End If&#xD;&#xA;Next&#xD;&#xA;arrListCodesUpdated = lstCodConSaldoBanco.ToArray()&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;' ============================================================&#xD;&#xA;' Paso 2: Asignar SALDO BOLETIN a SALDO BANCO si está vacío&#xD;&#xA;' ============================================================&#xD;&#xA;For Each row As System.Data.DataRow In dtBoletinTemp.Rows&#xD;&#xA;    Dim saldoBanco As String = row(&quot;SALDO BANCO&quot;).ToString().Trim()&#xD;&#xA;    If String.IsNullOrEmpty(saldoBanco) Then&#xD;&#xA;        row(&quot;SALDO BANCO&quot;) = row(&quot;SALDO BOLETIN&quot;).ToString().Trim()&#xD;&#xA;    End If&#xD;&#xA;Next&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;' ============================================================&#xD;&#xA;' Paso 3: Calcular DIFERENCIA = SALDO BOLETIN + VALORES X DIFERENCIAR - SALDO BANCO&#xD;&#xA;' ============================================================&#xD;&#xA;' Separador decimal = &quot;.&quot; | separador de miles = &quot;,&quot; (se elimina antes de parsear)&#xD;&#xA;Dim parsearDecimal As Func(Of String, Decimal) = Function(val As String) As Decimal&#xD;&#xA;    Dim clean As String = val.ToString().Trim().Replace(&quot;$&quot;, &quot;&quot;).Replace(&quot; &quot;, &quot;&quot;)&#xD;&#xA;    clean = clean.Replace(&quot;,&quot;, &quot;&quot;)  ' Eliminar separador de miles sin importar tamaño del número&#xD;&#xA;    Dim result As Decimal = 0&#xD;&#xA;    Decimal.TryParse(clean, System.Globalization.NumberStyles.Any, System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture, result)&#xD;&#xA;    Return result&#xD;&#xA;End Function&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;For Each row As System.Data.DataRow In dtBoletinTemp.Rows&#xD;&#xA;    Dim saldoBoletin As Decimal = parsearDecimal(row(&quot;SALDO BOLETIN&quot;).ToString())&#xD;&#xA;    Dim valoresDiferenciar As Decimal = parsearDecimal(row(&quot;VALORES X DIFERENCIAR&quot;).ToString())&#xD;&#xA;    Dim saldoBanco As Decimal = parsearDecimal(row(&quot;SALDO BANCO&quot;).ToString())&#xD;&#xA;    Dim diferencia As Decimal = saldoBoletin + valoresDiferenciar - saldoBanco&#xD;&#xA;    ' &quot;F2&quot; con InvariantCulture: siempre &quot;.&quot; como decimal, sin separadores de miles&#xD;&#xA;    ' Ejemplo: 1000060690983247.89 (nunca 1,000,060,690,983,247.89)&#xD;&#xA;    row(&quot;DIFERENCIA&quot;) = diferencia.ToString(&quot;F2&quot;, System.Globalization.CultureInfo.InvariantCulture)&#xD;&#xA;Next&#xD;&#xA;dtBoletinTemp.AcceptChanges()" DisplayName="Invoke Code - Calcular diferencia" sap:VirtualizedContainerService.HintSize="546,197" sap2010:WorkflowViewState.IdRef="InvokeCode_6">
